<br>
I'd love to have a way for all guilds to have a full plane.  But it isn't going to happen.  So either we <br>
<br>
1) Make Zenith have a completely empty plane for the first 3 hours they are up there and then deal with repops all night (err wait, we've done that to them forever now)<br>
<br>
or<br>
<br>
2) The guild that signs up after Zenith, knowing that Zenith will be running a late raid, has to adjust their start times. <br>
<br>
I'll take #2.<br>
<br>
If they don't want to adjust for the delayed start because of Zenith's prior reservation they have the option of NOT taking the date. <p><A HREF="http://www.silentredemption.org/" TARGET="_new">
